snippet: Rafael Nadal chalked up a double century of grand slam match wins by putting Argentine challenger Facundo Bagnis firmly in his place with a 6-3 6-0 6-3 demolition job in the second round of the French Open on Thursday....
lead_paragraph: Rafael Nadal chalked up a double century of grand slam match wins by putting Argentine challenger Facundo Bagnis firmly in his place with a 6-3 6-0 6-3 demolition job in the second round of the French Open on Thursday.

headline.print_headline: Nadal Downs Bagnis to Notch Up Double Century
headline.main: Nadal Downs Bagnis to Notch Up Double Century
